The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, surfing
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the italian##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | animation |
| Birthday   | october     | september      |
| Nationality   | japanese | italian   |
| Sport         | surfing  | badminton |

